parola auta entopisa oti ta eksis arxia "461","462","470" den leitourgoun, elegksa tis piges mou kai exoun to idio problima, den mpori na ginei kati giauta, sorry paides

Apisteutoi oi ellines, kathisa kai anebasa 27.07x2.5(nai diomisi fores! milame gia 67.68GB) kai oi parapano molis to katebasan stamatisan na to diamoirazoun. Pragmatika oi ellines ine GTP* (ntrepome pou me Ellinas, krima pou kai i xora mas ta idia xalia exi, o kathenas gia tin parti tou..)

Y.G. An ksanabgalo kanena episodio apo autin tin seira tripiste mou tin miti
GTP*= Gia Ton Po*ts0

Re file Crackez to katevasa olo edw kai 2 meres exw anevasei 11GB alla exw kolhsei sto 99.9% tou download kane kati kai gw tha to anevasw 20 fores oxi 2 se parakalw. A kai osa ida ine kai kali analhsh kai dn ine xalasmena :)

GRforce akoma prospathis?

an ine na ksethapso ta arxia gia na se boithiso, kapou prepei na ta xo
